==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Impuberty
<hw>Im*pu"ber*ty</hw> <pr>(-t⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
condition of not having reached puberty, or the age of ability to
reproduce one's species; lack of age at which the marriage contract can
be legally entered into.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impudence</ent>⟦br⟧
